{"tid":646333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解00後啲品味會咁差？係都要學一個低等國家嘅潮流文化？","createTime":"2018-04-29T02:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T15:46:57.000Z","uid":57376,"like":338,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"771b2f32704289412a8a6c54d789e79853f072cd","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"先唔講你班細路有無愛港心<br />\n喂個世界咁大，咁多優秀國家你唔學唔跟？<br />\n日本會差得過中國？德國美國會差得過中國？<br />\n老老實實如果你話你崇拜日本德國而放棄本土文化，我都仲覺得你起碼有啲眼光同品味<br />\n點撚知，屌！你居然為左學垃圾中國潮流而放棄香港，有無咁撚肉酸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國啵？果個柒完一千次都要繼續柒出國際嘅國家喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂，咁你要唔要學埋機場唱國歌抗議、同條女去公園跳廣場舞、排隊打尖、去旅行亂咁入人屋企、係外國文物上面寫到此一遊、然後！最緊要！入戲院睇《厲害了！我的國！》<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b71ecd4e45a69c7b49073b603358f900c16c23","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"有無00後入黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cf675f7df31f798bad8cb129ef8d8ab79124c8","tid":646333,"uid":75137,"like":69,"dislike":23,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"90後咪又係迷泡菜<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣咪又係落後過香港"},{"pid":"1756a573b07d86dd94f9313109602a876a4e1dcd","tid":646333,"uid":54927,"like":16,"dislike":63,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"打死都唔撚睇日本啦 咁撚毒"},{"pid":"ae35cd0e755087103a28074b505a2cd03ba1eef1","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"阿叔老啦<br />\n唔明白而家後生嘅品味<br />\n想搵個00後指點下中國潮流有咩優勝得過日本德國美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5516ec3a28fa96dfaf5ab5912fa1d31e64d32d2e","tid":646333,"uid":150230,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1756a573b07d86dd94f9313109602a876a4e1dcd","tid":646333,"uid":54927,"like":16,"dislike":63,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"打死都唔撚睇日本啦 咁撚毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"毒得過你睇蠓面超人"},{"pid":"22295b89ed426394e8310e9ddbc48ff5e186f402","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":62,"dislike":4,"score":58,"quote":{"pid":"06cf675f7df31f798bad8cb129ef8d8ab79124c8","tid":646333,"uid":75137,"like":69,"dislike":23,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"90後咪又係迷泡菜<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣咪又係落後過香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"但就連泡菜都好過中國啵<br />\n唔係中國就唔會跟啦<br />\n你睇而家幾多中國男明星係度扮韓仔<br />\n幾多大陸妹係度扮韓妹<br />\n點解唔係韓國學中國咁著衫同拍劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf8feffb8b32222cb9416d87cca3fe74135cac2","tid":646333,"uid":3454,"like":23,"dislike":8,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"上代香港人咪又係迷低質台風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排連登仲有個post懷念肉棒堂黑澀會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4442cc04b5d82d566b42ee36e7524611c6dcc5a4","tid":646333,"uid":143241,"like":15,"dislike":12,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"06cf675f7df31f798bad8cb129ef8d8ab79124c8","tid":646333,"uid":75137,"like":69,"dislike":23,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"90後咪又係迷泡菜<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣咪又係落後過香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"得啲垃圾賤種先會崇韓國呢啲藩屬國"},{"pid":"eca3033366db7a4726b7dfa6fd28574b16607b82","tid":646333,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae35cd0e755087103a28074b505a2cd03ba1eef1","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"阿叔老啦<br />\n唔明白而家後生嘅品味<br />\n想搵個00後指點下中國潮流有咩優勝得過日本德國美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl