islike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"坦白講，00後多左咁多大陸人，當中既仔仔女女都大個左，就算唔係雙非，真係南來人士，品質都唔會差過本土好多。<br />\n語言、文化相類似，習慣又差唔多，而且香港人又習慣左大時大節都要北上會親，佢地根本對北面係好親近既，相比美日法英德俄，取易不取難，係（短線地）合理呀。<br />\n根本你要佢地取難不取易，食女要食架／韓／鬼妹先係不切實際，脫離現實。"},{"pid":"ec7e31b15174b1f32907ee007b121cb9b4496df8","tid":646333,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46baf50b98684192dbf2c212b89ca30babda0a19","tid":646333,"uid":143241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ec7e31b15174b1f32907ee007b121cb9b4496df8","tid":646333,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"識佢老鼠咩"},{"pid":"a16ccc760acdae511a94f3a1ea1663ba52c0c4c1","tid":646333,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ae09b1d57723845558075647bb71a032f23fc86","tid":646333,"uid":79442,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"拿 我要留意下d八卦流行野同d office阿姐吹水， 咁韓日中台美都要睇。<br />\n有日我老婆見我睇韓國野就問我不如學韓文啦，我就同佢講 要學梗係學日文啦<br />\n中韓台流行文化 都會退熱，唯獨日本我出世到而家都未退過"},{"pid":"3129b9ba8a6dbef8f4b2a91206725e72729a9ab9","tid":646333,"uid":28786,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"強國同泡菜兩者比較，強國既野永遠有種 老土，造作，落後既感覺，洗唔甩個種柒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而泡菜最多都係柒同人造人，但都有返種時代感<br />\n<br />\n利伸：兩者都冇好感"},{"pid":"ea0c5b971357943867773b435fb0d624f73832f4","tid":646333,"uid":130466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"771b2f32704289412a8a6c54d789e79853f072cd","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"先唔講你班細路有無愛港心<br />\n喂個世界咁大，咁多優秀國家你唔學唔跟？<br />\n日本會差得過中國？德國美國會差得過中國？<br />\n老老實實如果你話你崇拜日本德國而放棄本土文化，我都仲覺得你起碼有啲眼光同品味<br />\n點撚知，屌！你居然為左學垃圾中國潮流而放棄香港，有無咁撚肉酸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國啵？果個柒完一千次都要繼續柒出國際嘅國家喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂，咁你要唔要學埋機場唱國歌抗議、同條女去公園跳廣場舞、排隊打尖、去旅行亂咁入人屋企、係外國文物上面寫到此一遊、然後！最緊要！入戲院睇《厲害了！我的國！》<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"因為班智障太難學語言，語言即文化。班死仆街仔成日林點解要學好英文，連學校規定教咁多年既英文都無本事學好，成日痴住本身既母語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52462395462d7223d62badd72b6e3fdc3237292f","tid":646333,"uid":3501,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"大陸明星真係好娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcc1c8de9475deb0060b2e0d1a87884b30e9863","tid":646333,"uid":60281,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"尤其係呢個年代<br />\ninternet乜都有得睇都要食垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82422f006ee23a5d12c23d7c8e404e418c66eb7e","tid":646333,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52462395462d7223d62badd72b6e3fdc3237292f","tid":646333,"uid":3501,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"大陸明星真係好娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"想學人又學唔足嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國歌影視文化幾乎全部要抄人<br />\n除左抗日神劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0444ae3b599e7f0e93e583d9a6d4f6f591b757ab","tid":646333,"uid":85819,"like":0,"